NAME

Data::Eacherator - simple each-list iterator generator for hashes and
arrays

SYNOPSIS

  use Data::Eacherator qw(eacherator);

  my $iter = eacherator($hash_or_array);
	 
  while (my ($k, $v) = $iter->()) {
      # ...
  }

PREREQUISITES

None.

